      "excerpt": "Company Profile Our Profile Company Profile Mediscan Labs, the only stand alone diagnostic centre in North Karnataka which is accredited by NABL in Medical Testing (National Accreditation Board for Testing and calibration Laboratories) & an ISO certified diagn...",
      "content": "Company Profile\nOur Profile\nMediscan Labs, the only stand alone diagnostic centre in North Karnataka which is accredited by NABL in Medical Testing (National Accreditation Board for Testing and calibration Laboratories) & an ISO certified diagnostic centre.\nMEDISCAN LABS commenced its operations on 5th April 1998, has consistently improved and upgraded its facilities with an aim to provide good, reliable diagnostic backup to the clinicians.\nMediscan Labs is situated in the heart of city of Gulbarga, would wish to highlight that, ours is the first diagnostic centre which is offering comprehensive range of diagnostic modalities by using the most sophisticated technology based equipments / machineries with Ultra Modern infrastructure facilities. We have completed 20 years & are successfully entering the third decade.\nRight from the beginning, we have always focused on Excellence, Transparency, Ethics, & Reliability.\nWe have services related to: Radiology, Cardiology, and Clinical Laboratory Medicine & Specialty Clinic to measure all aspect of Human Health & diagnose the problem right from the initial phase of the disease.\nVision\nTo provide excellent services to the needy patients, doctors, hospitals, nursing homes by providing them accurate results in reports\nMission\nThe vision shall be achieved by executing the parameters of Excellent Patient Care, TAT, Excellence, Transparent methods, Ethics, & Reliability\nOur Values\nExcellence in Clinical Testing w.r.to Radiology, Cardiology, & Clinical Testing Continuous improvement on SOP’s & technology up gradation\nOur Commitment\nWe always strive to be the BEST IN THE INDUSTRY by providing the Perfect Reports. We don’t compromise on our quality service at all….\n870 +\nSatisfied Patients\nMEDISCAN LABS has sole objective to provide trustworthy and high-quality laboratory service at a reasonable cost. Mediscan Labs has achieved the Vision by consistently accepting the need of the hour w.r.to change phenomenon. MEDISCAN LABS does not compromise on quality reagents, stringent external and internal quality evaluation and controls (IQC & EQAS).\nAs it is said that, Human Resource is the backbone of any organization.. the same is the case with MEDISCAN LABS having most qualified, dedicated & very professional team.\nMEDISCAN LABS is the first to use Dry Chemistry technology in Gulbarga region in the lab.\nMEDISCAN LABS has always proved that, they always prove their services as “Redefining Diagnostic Services” . We mean it, we prove it.\nMEDISCAN LABS also believes in continuous innovation w.r.to strategies to be implemented based on current market scenario, which really helps them to be always ahead of competition.",
