      "content": "Management\nOur Team\nManagement Team\nDr. Chetan Durgi\nMBBS, DMRD, MD\nDirector & Consultant Radiologist\nFacebook\nTwitter\nInstagram\nAbout Expert\nDr. Chetan S Durgi is the Chairman and Managing Director of Mediscan Labs, most advanced, fully automated and a very respectful Radiology in Karnataka State. Dr. Chetan S Durgi , a Radiologist with passion for hard work, vision to understand the future requirements, has element of taking high risks and motivates others to come along and join the journey or development with only one motive - Better Patient Care.\nHe did his MD in Radiology in the year 1980 form M.R. Medical College, Gulbarga. He had done his MBBS from the same college in the year 1977.\nUnder his expert guidance, Mediscan Labs has become one of the state of the Art Lab, having to its credit the highest certification and accreditation from the National Accreditation Board of Testing and Calibration Laboratories.\nThe lab has the capacity to test more than 1000 patients per day with its more than 5 labs spread all over state.\nHe gives highly specialized tests at minimal prices to the poor people and also organizes social cause events for the weaker section of the society every year.\nDr. Suchitra C Durgi is the Director and Consultant Radiologist of Mediscan Labs. Dr. Suchitra C Durgi , a Radiologist with passion for hard work, vision to understand the future requirements, has element of taking high risks and motivates others to come along and join the journey or development with only one motive - Better Patient Care.\nShe did her DMRD in Radiology in the year 1980 form M.R. Medical College, Gulbarga. She had done her MBBS from the same college in the year 1977.\nSkills\nConsultant's Expert\nWe merge two services consultant's and excellent nursing services.\nBetter Patient Care\nDr. Suchitra Durgi\nMBBS, DMRD",
