      "content": "Team of Empanelled Doctors\nOur Team\nDr. Vijaykumar Pattankar\nMBBS , MD, FICP, PGIMER\nFacebook\nTwitter\nInstagram\nAbout Expert\nA university topper throughout academics and Silver Medal Award Winner during MD.\nThe most renowned Pathologist in Gulbarga being serving the industry for past 40+ years.\n“Founder Fellow” on Indian College of Pathologist\n“External Expert / Advisor” in selection committee P.G.I.M.E.R. Chandigarh\n“External Expert / Reviewer” Philip Morris external research Program USA\nFormerly served as “Professor and HOD of Pathology” in M R Medical College, Gulbarga\n“KBNIMS & Faculty Medical Education Unit”\nPresented 155 papers in State & National Pathology Conferences 66 Guest Lectures in CME Programs Has special experience in Cardiac Pathology, Experimental Pathology, Oncopathology, Immunopathology, & Medical Education Technology.\nTrained in Advanced Microbiological Techniques (JIAMER Pondicherry), Advanced Microbiological Techniques (MAHE Manipal) & Molecular Techniques (MAMB Pune).\n“Associate Professor” in department of Microbiology in MR Medical College, Gulbarga Specialized in “Medical Microbiology”\nMember of Rapid response team of microbiology in Gulbarga district Resource person for “NACO” Certified “Internal Auditor for NABL”\nDr. Sunil Kumar Biradar\nMBBS, MD\nDr. S M Awanti\nConsultant Biochemist. MBBS, MD.\n(Department of biochemistry)\nDr. Veeramma N\nConsultant Pathologist. MBBS, MD.\n(Department of pathology)\nDr. Anand Kanaki\nConsultant. MBBS, MD.\n(Consultants)\nDr. P. V. Suresh\nVisiting consultant. MBBS, MD, DM\n(Cardiology)\nDr. S. M. Awanti\nAssociate Professor” in department of Microbiology in MR Medical College, Gulbarga Specialized in “Medical Microbiology”",
