      "link": "https://mediscanlab.com/directors-message",
      "excerpt": "Directors Message Dr. Chetan S Durgi Director & Consultant Radiologist Facebook Twitter Instagram MEDISCAN LABS Directors Message I am glad to highlight the growth of Mediscan Labs for past 20+ years which is exclusively based on the PERFECT REPORTS GENERATION...",
      "content": "Directors Message\nDr. Chetan S Durgi\nDirector & Consultant Radiologist\nFacebook\nTwitter\nInstagram\nMEDISCAN LABS\nI am glad to highlight the growth of Mediscan Labs for past 20+ years which is exclusively based on the PERFECT REPORTS GENERATION and the struggle put in by the entire staff team over the years.\nWe always focus on enriching the experience of patients which really help them to have total satisfaction on the reports generated. We always look ahead to develop the skills of the team by providing the excellent on job training based on technology & need-of-the-hour, which really help the them to do the best out of the services rendered.\nAs per today’s scenario on the criss-cross roads of the competition, we are always ahead, as the acceptance of the change for Mediscan is as simple as the daily routine work. We look at each of the change, as an big opportunity & take ahead with lot of courage & make it happen with highest level of efficiency, as per the demand of the hour.\nOur driving force has been passion for our work and commitment to our patient’s wellbeing. Over the span of 20+ years, our dedication towards our patients has not withered; instead it has given us strength and motivation to remain in step with the latest developments in this fast changing field, by periodically upgrading and modernizing tests and the lab. Professionally, maintaining the highest levels of quality and credibility has been central to our endeavor. We understand that the key to the proper medical treatment is the proper diagnosis which undoubtedly depends on how precise and accurate are test results given by the pathology lab. This is a huge challenge and we have embraced it with full conviction. We are proud to state that MEDISCAN LAB is the only PRIVATE lab in NORTH KARNATAKA accredited with both ISO and NABL.\nI truly and deeply appreciate the help of my team of doctors and employees who have always stood by me and worked with full commitment and unwavering enthusiasm towards the attainment of our goals. I would like to thank the patients for showing confidence in our professional abilities. Last but not the least, I would like to express my gratitude to the worthy practicing consultants of the state of KARNATAKA for the trust they repose on us.",
